
```
INDEX THE REFERENCE GENOME SEQUENCE

#Generate the index files for mapping

bwa index -a bwtsw hs37d5_chr22.fa 

#Generate the index files for picard and GATK

samtools faidx hs37d5_chr22.fa 

Generate the dictionary for GATK 

java -jar CreateSequenceDictionary.jar REFERENCE=hs37d5_chr22.fa OUTPUT=hs37d5_chr22.dict 

```
